Installation Instructions
*************************

Prerequisites:
- Make sure you are in project root directory

Build dependencies:
- GNU make
- GNU compatible C compiler

Make sure that all prerequisites are met and all dependencies are installed,
then run next command:
    make build

After that, using next command to install mewa for all users:
    ln -n ./bin/mewa /usr/local/bin/

Or, you can install only for one user:
    ln -n ./bin/mewa ~/.local/bin/